- You can't move or fire past islands or shipwrecks.<br>
- Pirates can be lured into colliding with islands shipwrecks or each other.<br>
- The pirate bosses never crash by accident and must be destroyed by cannons.<br>
- You get a bonus ship for every 1000 points you score.<br>
- On later levels watch out for the indestructible sea serpent.<br>
































































































































































